body_html: Hi @jubjamie @petewarden really appreciate your insights as I was also disturbed by the fact that the lib generated for Android is so large (more than 100MB). I am curiously what is the logic behind it? Why after compiled in Android Studio the lib size can be compressed so much? I think when I use selective registration I have already omit unnecessary ops?
